Results: gmd:identificationInfo.gmd:MD_DataIdentification.gmd:abstract.gco:CharacterString.#text:§This dataset is used to reproduce the analyses in manuscript "An approximate likelihood...." and contains the archive of the necessary material. Raw data consist in 4 sets of phylogenetic trees downloaded from the OrthoMam v10 (https://orthomam.mbb.cnrs.fr/) and UCSC Genome Browser (https://genome.ucsc.edu/) databases. The OrthoMam database was queried manually, selecting type = "exon" and setting no filter on fields "relative evolutionary rate", "%GC3", "alpha shape", et "alignment length". The UCSC query was passed via script ape_non_coding/download_all.bash
